\n依單野藍絲都冇野好講，除左無人性個班之外<br />\n<br />\n2. 繼續拉籠淺藍、中立同淺黃嘅市民<br />\n陰謀論，我覺得克警濫捕有部分目的係想轉移市民視線<br />\n唔好比市民忘記！<br />\n<br />\n3. 動搖建制勢力<br />\n將&quot;民賤聯=&gt;克警=&gt;黑社&quot; 講到11月區選<br />\n<br />\n4. 迫正苦去到懸崖邊<br />\n佢交人= 得罪鄉事建制勢力 + 克警失職<br />\n佢唔交 = 縱容黑社會治港 + 克警失職<br />\n佢拖 = 等於正苦無能，市民繼續屌<br />\n<br />\n佢交同唔交，都要成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n建議:<br />\n1. 我地會唔會係文宣加返重721比例？<br />\n2. 拜訪狗屋、民賤聯、支聯辦、正苦個陣唔好剩係屌佢老母，貼多啲支聯辦、正苦、民賤聯、克警、黑社會嘅關係圖，加721事件文宣<br />\n<br />\n點睇？"},{"pid":"b95754e737a1cf4a025b926273d7ff99a89a49d5","tid":1442312,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f71766319dfdec0255d30f64fdde53fe326c8bf","tid":1442312,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"幫10連推"},{"pid":"d2b9fd3ed155673178efe390f389bda5f847acbd","tid":1442312,"uid":261885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:03.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"faf585148066f6d9162dc5fb346d5faaa8391869","tid":1442312,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2c89e04d6bc5f815a6d1b5cfb9eb49a11b0abcca","tid":1442312,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"5868898ce1ddf50a1215a2ecac651806f316ffdf","tid":1442312,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f4f47da7c4f97bd10fd815420b2ecb4f0a477627","tid":1442312,"uid":262254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:49.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n警黑合作 <br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問"},{"pid":"8f7673fe2b1e871ab524a9ccfa92fba2e7f24b7b","tid":1442312,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4075176347c906437378deb15422cf392fb967be","tid":1442312,"uid":301394,"like":0,"di